{"tid":856343,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【施政後成交】大興花園2期劈足「1球」僅售450萬","createTime":"2018-10-10T14:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T14:16:40.000Z","uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73c6e403d7d9cece5878571882b1d28661b873e1","tid":856343,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"2018年10月10日 <br />\n<br />\n【施政後成交】大興花園2期劈足「1球」僅售450萬 <br />\n<br />\n施政報告後屯門錄第一宗劈價。<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產胡志偉表示，屯門大興花園2期錄減價成交，3座中層H室，實用面積419方呎，上月叫價550萬元放盤，早兩星期已經有買家還價470萬元，但當時業主觀望市場變化放棄，及後市場反應冷淡，直至今天施政報告公佈，即晚累減100萬至450萬元終沽出，呎價10,740元。<br />\n<br />\n大興花園2期同面積單位高位成交，為9座高層H室，今年6月造價535萬元，呎價12,768元。是次造價重返年初水平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181010/large/1539179641_c8bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F1539179641_c8bf.jpg&h=e4d043e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181010/58780206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58780206&d=LyEjm9il6BC0muFEPB%2B4C5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3a37009c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58780206&h=f4f848c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181010/58780206</a>"},{"pid":"a67790e7bbb93f9fe69eb020b529e3c81d1c5d87","tid":856343,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"屯門唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3486c07bd92948393af9689c89229e1922e70e","tid":856343,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"跌左成萬點 減少少都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a4d